text: The 1917 Kentucky Wildcats football team represented the Kentucky Wildcats of the University of Kentucky during the 1917 college football season.https://www.sports- reference.com/cfb/schools/kentucky/1917-schedule.html The season ended on a high note with the 52-0 defeat of Florida. ==Schedule== ==References== Kentucky Category:Kentucky Wildcats football seasons
